<div class="callout-box">
    <h3><a href="http://www.pensionrights.org/">The Pension Rights Center</a></h3>
    <p>The Pension Rights Center is the nation's only consumer organization dedicated solely to protecting and promoting the retirement security of American workers, retirees, and their families. <a href="http://www.pensionrights.org/">Visit the PRC website</a>.</p>
</div>
<div class="callout-box">
    <h3><a href="/help/resources#counseling_projects">The Pension Counseling &amp; Information Program</a></h3>
    <p>Funded by the U.S. Administration on Aging, six regional Pension Counseling projects help individuals understand their pension rights and claim the benefits they have earned, regardless of age or income. Services are provided free of charge. <%= link_to 'Learn more', '/help/resources#counseling_projects' %>.</p>
</div>
<div class="callout-box">
    <h3><a href="/help/resources">Learn About Our Service Partner Network</a></h3>
    <p>PensionHelp America connects individuals looking for answers to questions about their retirement plan to the resources that can help them. <%= link_to 'Learn more', '/help/resources' %>.</p>
</div>
<div class="callout-box">
    <h3><a href="/works">Attention: Pension Professionals</a></h3>
    <p>Join one of our PensionHelp networks if you are a pension lawyer, actuary, or other pension professional.  <%= link_to 'Learn more', '/works' %>.</p>
</div>
